name: Minecraft Classic Level Editor
body:
# MCLE
Minecraft Classic Level Editor

#MCLE Installing

1. Download JDK (Java Developoment Kit).
2. Paste minecraft-server.jar to MCLE.
3. Complir MCLE.
4. Run MCLE on cmd.
5. Enjoy!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
